Title: A lost soul who find the way in Portugal
DateModified: '2019-03-02'
DatePublished: '2019-03-02'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/a-lost-soul-who-find-the-way-in-portugal
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Valentina  Ortega domenino
AuthorCountry: Argentina
Text: "All begins with an Argentina girl, she was around 25 years old. Her really\
  \ love ( or that\u2019s she thinks) never give her the opportunity of give all the\
  \ love that she has inside. Almost that, her college live isn\u2019t the best one:\
  \ she study business only couse that was her fathers dream. She tried to find her\
  \ soul so many times but with out luck. She was wondering how to make a difference,\
  \ how to find the happiness traveling and meeting people who give brilliant light\
  \ to her sold and helps her in the way to find herself.the better place to do that\
  \ was the colorful streets of Portugal, the beautiful kind of people she meet there,\
  \  the experience of being she and just she in front of the word"
